subject: shellcheck: clean up shellcheck warnings
commitMessage:
shellcheck: clean up shellcheck warnings

Shellcheck reports significant issues with the shell scripts in
this repository.  Clean them all up by following shellcheck
recommendations or squashing the warning in a few specific
cases.

Signed-off-by: Patrick Williams <patrick@stwcx.xyz>
Change-Id: Id90c4808af04135fec28d192b4fd3b5beda49a1f
